# Tableau Project forward steps 

## Step 1: Analyse Requirement
- Collect requirements
- Choose appropriate charts
- Draw mockups
- Select colors

## Step 2: Build Data Source
- Connect to data
- Create data model
- Rename fields in tables
- Check data types
- Understand the data

## Step 3: Build Charts
- Create calculated fields if needed
- Build charts
- Format charts
- Maintain grid lines
- Clean up axis headers
- Apply coloring
- Configure tooltips

## Step 4: Build Dashboard
- Draw mockup for container layout
- Create container structure
- Place all charts together
- For multiple charts, distribute objects evenly
- Format colors, size, and styles
- Fit "entire view" to screen
- Add legends
- Add spaces (inner/outer padding)
- Add dynamic filters
- Add icons
